<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
step 1 - swap the ```k```th column values to ```0```th column values.
step 2 - sort the ```score``` using customised compare function whose condition is ```v1[0] > v2[0]```.
step 3 - swap ```0```th column values back to ```k```th column values.
step 4 - return the ```score``` vector.

